National Energy Board Act Part VI (Oil and Gas) Regulations
SubjectIssuance of Licence GL-335 - WCC LNG Ltd.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-335 to WCC LNG Ltd. to export natural gas, in the form of liquefied natural gas, from a point at the outlet of the loading arm of the natural gas liquefaction terminal to be located in the vicinity of either Kitimat or Prince Rupert, British Columbia.
